Changelog for Abc.

vNEXT

  Internal changes.
  * Unless specified otherwise, projects in the folder "test" now use an exact
    version match to resolve the package Abc.Maybe.
  * eng\pack.ps1:
    - Always set ContinuousIntegrationBuild to true

2020-06-16, version 1.0.2

  Visible changes.
  * Removed "net452"; use "netstandard1.1" instead (should happen automatically).

  Internal changes.
  * Set up GitHub actions and Azure Pipelines. The main outcome is that the
    tests now execute on Windows, Linux and MacOS.
  * Always enable "coverlet.collector" and only reference "coverlet.msbuild"
    when explicitly requested.
  * When enabled, Source Link now processes all projects in "src".
  * Tweak package and platform selections for projects src\Abc.Tests and
    test\Package (see "src\Abc.Tests\D.B.targets").
  * eng\harness.cmd: new script to quickly run the test suite.
  * Upgraded dependencies:
    - xunit.runner.visualstudio 2.4.1 -> 2.4.2.
    - dotnet-reportgenerator-globaltool 4.5.8 -> 4.6.1.

2020-05-31, version 1.0.1

  Visible changes.
  * For older Windows-only platforms, use "pdbonly" instead of "portable".

  Internal changes.
  * eng\freeze-api.ps1: handle the annotation "#nullable enable".
  * eng\cover.ps1: when using Coverlet, include the platform name in the output
    filename.
  * eng\pack.ps1:
    - Disable Source Link when there are uncommited changes.
    - Remove the timestamp from the informational version.
  * asm.ps1: new script to retrieve informations about an assembly.
  * Upgraded packages:
    - coverlet.msbuild 2.8.1 -> 2.9.0.

2020-05-27, version 1.0.0

  First stable release.

2017-04-07, version 0.28.0

  Still available on nuget.org but under a different name
  [https://www.nuget.org/packages/Narvalo.Fx/], this package is now deprecated.

